---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Harvesting Ethics | VA.INDEX">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-blueberry-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">HARVESTING ETHICS</h1>
      <p class="text-blueberry-800/60 font-medium">Protocol v3.0 — The Goldilocks Standard</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-blueberry-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">01. Public-First Access</h2>
        <p class="text-blueberry-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          VA.INDEX only consumes data from publicly available RSS, Atom, and JSON feeds. We specifically target channels that job boards and employers intentionally publish for syndication. We do not bypass authentication, scrape private data, or circumvent access controls.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-blueberry-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">02. Respectful Cadence</h2>
        <p class="text-blueberry-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          We operate on a "Goldilocks" schedule — neither too fast to be disruptive, nor too slow to be stale. Our fleet of ethical harvesters uses staggered cadences and global locking to ensure we never overwhelm a source with redundant requests.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-blueberry-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">03. Transparent Identity</h2>
        <p class="text-blueberry-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Every request from our fleet identifies itself via a custom User-Agent header: <code class="bg-oat-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold text-blueberry-900">VA-Hub-Harvester</code>. This header includes a direct link to this policy, allowing administrators to verify our intent and contact us if needed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-blueberry-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">04. Mutual Benefit</h2>
        <p class="text-blueberry-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Our goal is to drive high-intent, qualified Filipino remote workers directly to the original job listings. We do not re-host full content or "steal" traffic; we act as a high-velocity discovery engine that preserves the value and attribution of the source platforms.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-oat-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-black text-blueberry-600 hover:text-blueberry-900 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest">← Return to Index</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
